I didn't find it believable at first,
一开始我觉得不可信

693
00:51:09,280 --> 00:51:11,080
but I think they might've had a point.
但我现在认为他们说的有点道理

694
00:51:11,640 --> 00:51:16,560
They said that conscience resembles the gut.
他们说良心很像内心

695
00:51:17,640 --> 00:51:19,480
And the gut resembles conscience.
内脏就像良心

696
00:51:20,080 --> 00:51:24,320
If you want it emptied, you have to be the one to do it.
如果你想让它空出来，你就必须自杀

697
00:51:25,600 --> 00:51:28,080
Funny. See...
很有趣  你看……

698
00:51:29,440 --> 00:51:31,120
I prepared this for you.
我为你准备了这个

699
00:51:31,800 --> 00:51:33,480
To stick on your forehead.
贴在额头上

700
00:51:33,560 --> 00:51:36,120
But since you're going to be the one to do it,
但是既然你将要自杀了

701
00:51:36,200 --> 00:51:37,840
I wouldn't want to disrespect you.
我不想不尊重你

702
00:51:38,480 --> 00:51:41,920
I wouldn't want to get between you and your conscience.
我不想介于你和你的良心之间

703
00:51:42,000 --> 00:51:44,320
That's why I won't.
那就是我不会干涉你的原因

704
00:51:46,200 --> 00:51:47,080
Go on.
继续

705
00:51:47,160 --> 00:51:50,600
I wonder which of us is the crazier one. Leave me alone.
我想知道我们中谁是最疯狂的  走开！

706
00:51:53,040 --> 00:51:56,720
- Would you like some help? - Stay right there!
-你需要帮助吗？-别过来！

707
00:51:56,800 --> 00:51:58,920
Sure. But don't tarry.
当然可以，但别拖延了

708
00:51:59,600 --> 00:52:02,040
The cops are looking for you. They might be here soon.
警察正在找你  他们可能很快就会来

709
00:52:20,200 --> 00:52:25,280
Make it quick. Raise yourself. Just like this, see?
快点  把自己吊起来，就像这样，懂吗？

710
00:52:25,360 --> 00:52:28,480
Not like that. Get on your tippy-toes.
不是那样的，小心点

711
00:52:29,440 --> 00:52:30,440
That's it!
对了！

712
00:52:31,200 --> 00:52:32,280
Let yourself go!
松手把！

713
00:52:33,280 --> 00:52:37,840
Kill yourself and be done with it. No more pangs of conscience, Ufuk.
结束自己的生命吧  不再有良心的痛苦  乌福克

714
00:52:37,920 --> 00:52:39,440
Go on, don't be scared.
继续，不要害怕

715
00:52:40,080 --> 00:52:41,120
Go on!
继续！

716
00:52:44,120 --> 00:52:45,520
Where are you?
哪去了？

717
00:53:03,640 --> 00:53:05,320
It's funny.
真有趣

718
00:53:06,600 --> 00:53:09,400
This is exactly how I taught my daughter to swim.
这正是我教我女儿游泳的方法

719
00:53:10,800 --> 00:53:11,960
We were in Erdek.
我们在埃尔德克

720
00:53:12,800 --> 00:53:14,920
She was on the pontoon. I was in the water.
她在船上  我在水里

721
00:53:15,520 --> 00:53:17,720
I kept telling her to jump.
我让她跳下来

722
00:53:19,640 --> 00:53:21,560
She refused to do it.
她不跳

723
00:53:21,640 --> 00:53:24,400
I told her I was right there, there was nothing to be scared of.
我告诉她我就在那里，没有什么可害怕的

724
00:53:27,080 --> 00:53:29,400
Come on, come to papa.
来吧，到爸爸这来

725
00:53:32,640 --> 00:53:33,800
Let yourself go.
放自己走

726
00:53:34,520 --> 00:53:35,920
Come on in.
来吧

727
00:53:40,080 --> 00:53:43,040
That's it! That was some jump.
就是这样！

728
00:53:44,600 --> 00:53:46,120
Zuhal wouldn't jump.
祖哈尔不会跳

729
00:53:48,000 --> 00:53:49,920
She just froze.
她只是呆在那里

730
00:53:50,000 --> 00:53:53,080
My little girl wouldn't trust her father.
我的小女儿不相信她的父亲

731
00:53:57,080 --> 00:53:59,040
She was wise beyond her years.
她拥有她的年龄不应拥有的智慧

732
00:55:11,480 --> 00:55:15,000
DOG SLAYER
狗杀手

